[148.403962, "o", "❯ Run a feature-planning workflow for adding a --verbose flag to this CLI. First surface the workflow-level\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K  acceptance criteria. Then run two stages: an explore stage that maps where argument parsing and output happen,\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K  and a plan stage that drafts an ordered implementation approach — threading each stage into your workflow\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K  dossier. Then FINALIZE as :partial. Do NOT run an exec stage and do NOT write any code into the project — this\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K  is recommend-only. Take the finalize as a deliberate two-step (helper fence, then the answer with your\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K  contract line).\u001b[0m\u001b[25;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(8.5s)\u001b[0m\u001b[26;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;96m+\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 2 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(52318 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(2m 12s)\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mTurn 1, no real history. The user wants a feature-planning workflow for adding a --verbose flag. I \u001b[0m\u001b[28;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mneed to: bootstrap the dossier first, surface ac"]
[148.403989, "o", "ceptance criteria, then run explore + plan stages, \u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mthen FINALIZE as :partial (two-step). No exec, recommend-only. Step 1: Resolve template. Let me list \u001b[0m\u001b[30;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mtemplates and find a feature-planning / feature-launch fit. Compute deterministic id, probe resume, \u001b[0m\u001b[31;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mthen bootstrap. I'll do this in one clojure fence to gather template + id + resume state first, then \u001b[0m\u001b[32;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mbootstrap based on what's available. Let me start by discovering templates and computing the id.\u001b[0m\u001b[33;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;93m⠼\u001b[0m\u001b[2m]\u001b[0m \u001b[96mPondering...\u001b[0m\u001b[2m (2m 20s)\u001b[0m"]
