[301.102082, "o", "After bootstrap \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mI'll surface acceptance in the next step. Doing bootstrap now in one fence.\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m• Code:\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m┌─\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m;; feature-launch template not found → go :ad-hoc with hand-drafted acceptance + stages.\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(def wid (:slug (workflow$id :template :ad-hoc\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m                             :question \"Run a feature-planning workflow for adding a --verbose flag to\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mthis CLI\")))\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(println \"WID:\" wid)\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(def acceptance\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  [{:id \"a1\" :text \"Where CLI argument parsing happens is mapped with concrete file/line pointers.\"\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m:status :open}\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m   {:id \"a2\" :text \"Where output/printing happens is mapped with concrete file/line pointers.\" :status\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m:open}\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m   {:id \"a3\" :text \"An ordered, recommend-o"]
[301.102092, "o", "nly implementation approach for a --verbose flag is drafted\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mand cited (no code written into the project).\" :status :open}])\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(def stages\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  [{:id \"explore-parsing-output\"\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m    :agent \"explore-agent\"\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m    :purpose \"Map where CLI argument parsing and output/printing happen in this project, with file/line\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mpointers.\"\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m    :acceptance-focus [\"a1\" \"a2\"]\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m    :status :pending}\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m   {:id \"plan-verbose-flag\"\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m    :agent \"plan-agent\"\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m    :purpose \"Draft an ordered, recommend-only implementation approach for adding a --verbose flag,\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mgrounded in the explore findings.\"\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m    :acceptance-focus [\"a3\"]\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m[*Block:i4sf1blcode* collapse"]
